Detailed Description

abstract domain visitor interface

This class defines the abstract interface used to implement a visitor of TREX domains (aka DomainBase)

It allows to visit different standard types of domain and embeds a default behavior for classes that do not inherit from these.

See also:
void DomainBase::accept(DomainVisitor &)
